{
  "text": "Specific complications were associated with different methods of arthrodesis. While implant failure and hardware breakage affected 6.9% and 7.7% of IMN cases in 2 studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , pin site infections complicated 0.5-100% of EF arthrodesis. Mean operative time up to 6 hours with more than 2.9 L of blood replacement requirements has also been recorded following IMN arthrodesis for PJI [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "24918269",
